title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H3 - Jun 25 2022
itunes:title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H3 - Jun 25 2022
description:
Biden's gas tax holiday is a gimmick, Barack Obama said so in 2008. Clay predicts Floridian Trump vs. Floridian DeSantis "major battle" for GOP nomination in 2024, so does Politico. Also: Powerhouse DeSantis won't request Trump's gubernatorial endorsement. C&B dive into indictment against former Florida gubernatorial candidate Andrew Gillum arrested on wire fraud charges. Elon Musk agrees with C&B: Recession likely. Clay, in recognition of the show's one-year anniversary this week, reads list of C&B #1 markets.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
